(97, 1, '2013-08-06 19:17:11', '2013-08-06 19:17:11', '<strong>Welcome to the political framing website. This site is currently under construction as I am uploading details of version 1.0. - This should be done by tomorrow (Wednesday 8/7) evening. Thank you for your patience, please come back soon to see the latest revision!\r\n</strong>\r\nThis project is an attempt to understand the rhetorical framing of political speeches computationally. Please find the the following links to the <a href="//www.politicalframing.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Final-Report-Draft.pdf">initial paper</a> and to the <a href="http://www.politicalframing.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/DRSpeechData.xlsx">initial output-data</a> of the project, explained in the sections below. <table  border="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr> <td> \r\n<iframe src="https://skydrive.live.com/embed?cid=E72FCA9FDC2435F6&amp;resid=E72FCA9FDC2435F6%21430&amp;authkey=AAMZAdQeRjeptTg&amp;em=2&amp;wdAr=1.3333333333333332" height="360" width="610" frameborder="0"></iframe></td>\r\n<td valign="left"> \r\n<h2><a href="http://www.politicalframing.com/?page_id=45#motivation"><center>Motivation</center></a>\r\n<a href="http://www.politicalframing.com/?page_id=45#methodology"><center>Methodology</center></a>\r\n<a href="http://www.politicalframing.com/?page_id=45#dataandresults"><center>Data and Results</center></a>\r\n<a href="http://www.politicalframing.com/?page_id=45#conclusions"><center>Conclusions</center></a>\r\n<a href="http://www.politicalframing.com/?page_id=45#references"><center>References</center></a></h2>\r\n<center>Provide feedback at <strong> dhrumil [dot] mehta [at] gmail.com </strong> \r\nvisit me at <a href="http://www.dhrumilmehta.com" target="_blank">www.dhrumilmehta.com</a></center>\r\n</td></tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>', 'Project Summary', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '5-revision-v1', '', '', '2013-08-06 19:17:11', '2013-08-06 19:17:11', '', 5, 'http://www.politicalframing.com/?p=97', 0, 'revision',